PROJECT 1 - SECURITY AUDIT/README.md

Security Audit - Controls and Compliance Checklist
📌 Objective
Conduct a security audit using a controls and compliance checklist.  
The goal was to understand how to identify strengths and weaknesses in an organization’s security posture against best practices and compliance requirements.
🛠️ What Was Done
⦁	Studied key security and compliance frameworks
⦁	Applied a checklist of controls to evaluate compliance
⦁	Documented results and identified gaps
⦁	Reflected on corrective actions and recommended improvements
📚 Reference Materials
⦁	PDF: Supporting Materials For Activity 1
🎯 Key Learning
Learned how to apply security checklists to conduct a basic audit, identifying areas of compliance and gaps that need to be addressed to ensure stronger information security.
